{"tid":924134,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"山齊士愛狗愛到「強逼症」？","createTime":"2018-12-01T23:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T23:29:50.000Z","uid":216021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc074627145c0186520d026d877348a08bd5a6f","tid":924134,"uid":216021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T23:25:31.000Z","msg":"「狗奴」阿歷斯山齊士深愛家中幾隻寵物犬眾所周知，但有網民發現他的愛似是有點兒過火。<br />\n阿歷斯山齊士（Alexis Sanchez）日前因傷留家休養，將自己的復康照片放上社交網站。照片中見山神正在使用復康儀器，愛犬伏在身邊看著自己，原本一切都正常不過。但有眼利的網民發現放在遠處的相架當中有幾張「山神與狗」的照片，而且奇怪地同一張照片出現兩次！有網民就認為是山齊士愛犬已達「強逼症」的境界，才會做出如此古怪行為。 早前曼聯主帥摩連奴談及山齊士的傷情時，一如既往「挑機」，認為傳媒一定會猜度山齊士與他不和被「雪藏」。如今有相為證，山齊士確是正在復康，或會打消不少外間的流言蜚語。而這位智利攻擊球員因肌肉傷患問題，或需缺陣直到2019年年初方能復出，錯過聖誕英超賽期。"},{"pid":"379ab563237f29ecb67b4d5ed064f8781a144e9e","tid":924134,"uid":216021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T23:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2016/08/22/11/377C073B00000578-0-image-a-76_1471860020257.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2016%2F08%2F22%2F11%2F377C073B00000578-0-image-a-76_1471860020257.jpg&h=1aa179bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/12/atom-humber.png?quality=90&amp;strip=all&amp;zoom=1&amp;resize=644%2C576\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmetrouk2.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F12%2Fatom-humber.png%3Fquality%3D90%26strip%3Dall%26zoom%3D1%26resize%3D644%252C576&h=b4fff67c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"021f760ef1ab045fd720e2c266e3609c3dfcb68d","tid":924134,"uid":15830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T23:29:01.000Z","msg":"全能到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d85fbccee8514caa3f62c57538739c86932aa3","tid":924134,"uid":216021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T23:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SPORT-PREVIEW-sanchez-dogs-picture.jpg?strip=all&amp;quality=100&amp;w=750&amp;h=500&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FSPORT-PREVIEW-sanchez-dogs-picture.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26quality%3D100%26w%3D750%26h%3D500%26crop%3D1&h=fc23f440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}